  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Front of House",
  "description": "<p><strong>Front of House (FOH) – Gym & Yoga Studio</strong></p><p>We’re looking for a friendly and proactive Front of House (FOH) staff to manage daily front desk operations and create a welcoming experience for our members.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Greet members and handle walk-in enquiries</p></li><li><p>Manage check-ins, bookings, calls, and WhatsApp messages</p></li><li><p>Assist with memberships, payments, and basic admin</p></li><li><p>Create simple content using <strong>Canva / CapCut</strong> (basic posters, short videos, stories)</p></li><li><p>Support daily studio operations and maintain front desk area</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Pleasant personality with good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Comfortable using <strong>Canva, CapCut, or basic video editing apps</strong></p></li><li><p>Basic computer skills</p></li><li><p>Customer service experience preferred</p></li><li><p>Able to work shifts and weekends</p></li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Free access to yoga classes and gym usage</strong></p></li><li><p>Supportive and fun work environment</p></li></ul>",
